quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  33,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  33,1,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! Allah se daro aur kufar o munafiqeen ki itaat nah karo, haqeeqat mein Aleem aur hakeem to Allah hi hai"
  33,2,"pairwi karo uss baat ki jis ka ishara tumahray rab ki taraf se tumhe kya ja raha hai, Allah har uss baat se bakhabar hai jo tum log karte ho"
  33,3,"Allah par tawakkal karo, Allah hi wakeel honay ke liye kaafi hai"
  33,4,"Allah ne kisi shakhs ke dhar mein do dil nahi rakhay hain, nah is ne tum logon ki unn biwion ko jin se tum zhar karte ho tumhari maa bana diya hai, aur nah is ne tumahray mun bolay beton ko tumhara haqeeqi beta banaya hai yeh to woh baatein hain jo tum log apne mun se nikaal dete ho, magar Allah woh baat kehta hai jo mabni Bar haqeeqat hai, aur wohi sahih tareeqay ki taraf rahnumai karta hai"
  33,5,"mun bolay beton ko un ke bapon ki nisbat se poukaro, yeh Allah ke nazdeek ziyada munsifana baat hai aur agar tumhe maloom nah ho ke un ke baap kon hain to woh tumahray dainee bhai aur Rafeeq hain na danista jo baat tum kaho is ke liye tum par koi girift nahi hai, lekin uss baat par zaroor girift hai jis ka tum dil se iradah karo Allah dar guzar karne wala aur Raheem hai"
  33,6,"bilashuba nabi to ahal imaan ke liye unn ki apni zaat par muqaddam hai, aur nabi ki biwiyan unn ki maaen hain, magar kitaab Allah ki ro se aam momnin o muhajreen ki bah nisbat rishta daar aik dosray ke ziyada haqdaar hain, Albata apne rfiqon ke sath tum koi bhalai ( karna chaho to ) kar satke ho yeh hukum kitaab Ellahi mein likha howa hai"
  33,7,"aur ( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) yaad rakho uss ehad o Paiman ko jo hum ne sab payghambaroon se liya hai, tum se bhi aur Nooh aur ibrahim aur moose aur eesa Ibn maryam se bhi sab se hum pukhta ehad le chuke hain"
  33,8,"taakay sachey logon se ( un ka rab ) un ki sachaai ke baray mein sawal kere, aur kafiroon ke liye to is ne dard naak azaab muhayya kar hi rakha hai"
  33,9,"ae logo, jo imaan laaye ho, yaad karo Allah ke ahsaan ko jo ( abhi abhi ) uss ne tum par kya hai jab lashkar tum par charh aeye to hum ne unn par aik sakht aandhi bhaij di aur aisi faujein rawana kee jo tum ko nazar nah aati theen Allah woh sab kuch dekh raha tha jo tum log is waqt kar rahay thay"
  33,10,"jab woh ooper se aur neechay se tum par charh aeye jab khauf ke maaray ankhen pathra gayeen, kaleje mun ko aa gay, aur tum log Allah ke baray mein terhan terhan ke gumaan karne lagey"
  33,11,uss waqt imaan laane walay khoob aazamaa_e gay aur burii terhan hila maaray gay
  33,12,yaad karo woh waqt jab munafiqeen aur woh sab log jin ke dilon mein rog tha saaf saaf keh rahay thay ke Allah aur uss ke Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ne jo waday hum se kiye thay woh fraib ke siwa kuch nah thay
  33,13,"jab unn mein se aik giroh ne kaha ke"" ae Yasrab ke logo, tumahray liye ab ٹھیرنے ka koi mauqa nahi hai, palat chalo"" jab un ka aik fareeq yeh keh kar NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam se rukhsat talab kar raha tha ke"" hamaray ghar khatray mein hain,"" halaank woh khatray mein nah thay, darasal woh ( mahaaz jung se ) bhagna chahtay thay"
  33,14,agar shehar ke atraaf se dushman ghis aeye hotay aur uss waqt inhen ftne ki taraf dawat di jati to yeh is mein ja parte aur mushkil hi se inhen shareek fitnah honay mein koi tamil hota
  33,15,"un logon ne is se pehlay Allah se ehad kya tha ke yeh peeth nah phairen ge, aur Allah se kiye hue ehad ki baz purse to honi hi thi"
  33,16,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! un se kaho, agar tum mout ya qatal se bhago to yeh bhagna tumahray liye kuch bhi naffa bakhash nah ho ga is ke baad zindagi ke mazay lotney ka thora hi mauqa tumhe mil sakay ga"
  33,17,"inn se kaho, kon hai jo tumhe Allah se bacha sakta ho agar woh tumhe nuqsaan pahunchana chahay? aur kon is ki rehmat ko rok sakta hai agar woh tum par meharbani karna chahay? Allah ke muqablay mein to yeh log koi haami o madad gaar nahi pa satke hain"
  33,18,"Allah tum mein se unn logon ko khoob jaanta hai jo ( jung ke kaam mein ) rakawaten daalnay walay hain, jo apne bhaiyon se kehte hain ke"" aao hamari taraf"" jo larai mein hissa letay bhi hain to bas naam gunane ko"
  33,19,"jo tumhara sath dainay mein sakht bukheel hain khatray ka waqt aa jaye to is terhan daiday phira phira kar tumhari taraf dekhte hain jaisay kisi marnay walay par ghashi taari ho rahi ho, magar jab khatrah guzar jata hai to yahi log faido ke harees ban kar qainchi ki terhan chalti hui zubanain liye tumahray istaqbaal ko aa jatay hain yeh log hargiz imaan nahi laaye, isi liye Allah ne un ke saaray aamaal zaya kar diye aur aisa karna Allah ke liye bohat aasaan hai"
  33,20,yeh samajh rahay hain ke hamla aawar giroh abhi gay nahi hain aur agar woh phir hamla aawar ho jayen to un ka jee chahta hai ke uss mauqa par yeh kahin sehraa mein bdoon ke darmain ja bathain aur wahein se tumahray halaat puchhte rahen taham agar yeh tumahray darmain rahay bhi to larai mein kam hi hissa len ge
  33,21,"Dur haqeeqat tum logon ke liye Allah ke Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam mein aik behtareen namona tha, har uss shakhs ke liye jo Allah aur yom aakhir ka umeed waar ho aur kasrat se Allah ko yaad kere"
  33,22,"aur sachey mominon ( ka haal uss waqt yeh tha ke ) jab unhon ne hamla aawar lashkaron ko dekha to pukaar utthay ke"" yeh wohi cheez hai jis ka Allah aur is ke rasool ne hum se wada kya tha, Allah aur uss ke Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ki baat bilkul sachhi thi"" iss waqea ne unn ke imaan aur un ki supurdagi ko aur ziyada barha diya"
  33,23,imaan laane walon mein aisay log mojood hain jinhon ne Allah se kiye hue ehad ko sacha kar dekhaya hai un mein se koi apni Nazar poori kar chuka aur koi waqt anay ka muntazir hai unhon ne apne ravayye mein koi tabdeeli nahi ki
  33,24,"( yeh sab kuch is liye howa ) taakay Allah schon ko unn ki sachaai ki jaza day aur munafiqon ko chahay to saza day aur chahay to un ki tauba qubool kar le, be shak Allah ghafoor o Raheem hai"
  33,25,"Allah ne kufar ka mun phair diya, woh koi faida haasil kiye baghair apne dil ki jalan liye yuhin palat gay, aur momnin ki taraf se Allah hi larnay ke liye kaafi ho gaya, Allah barri qowat wala aur zabardast hai"
  33,26,"phir ahal kitaab mein se jin logon ne un hamla awaron ka sath diya tha, Allah un ki gurhiyun se inhen utaar laya aur unn ke dilon mein uss ne aisa Roab daal diya ke aaj un mein se aik giroh ko tum qatal kar rahay ho aur dosray giroh ko qaid kar rahay ho"
  33,27,is ne tum ko un ki zameen aur un ke gharon aur un ke amwal ka waris bana diya aur woh ilaqa tumhe diya jisay tum ne kabhi pamaal nah kya tha Allah har cheez par Qadir hai
  33,28,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, apni biwion se kaho, agar tum duniya aur is ki zeenat chahti ho to aao, mein tumhe kuch day dila kar bhallay tareeqay se rukhsat kar dun"
  33,29,aur agar tum Allah aur is ke Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam aur daar akhirat ki taalib ho to jaan lau ke tum mein se jo naiko car hain Allah ne un ke liye bara ajar muhayya kar rakha hai
  33,30,"NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ki byoyo, tum mein se jo kisi Sarih fehash harkat ka irtikaab kere gi usay dohra azaab diya jaye ga, Allah ke liye yeh bohat aasaan kaam hai"
  33,31,aur tum mein se jo Allah aur uss ke Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ki itaat kere gi aur naik amal kere gi is ko hum dohra ajar den ge aur hum ne is ke liye rizaq kareem muhayya kar rakha hai
  33,32,"NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ki byoyo, tum aam aurton ki terhan nahi ho agar tum Allah se darny wali ho to dubi zabaan se baat nah kya karo ke dil ki kharabi ka mubtala koi shakhs lalach mein par jaye, balkay saaf seedhi baat karo"
  33,33,"apne gharon mein tِk kar raho aur sabiq daur jahliat ki si sajh dhaj nah dukhati phiro namaz qaim karo, zkoh do aur Allah aur uss ke Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ki itaat karo Allah to yeh chahta hai ke ehley beeet NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam se gandagi ko daur kere aur tumhe poori terhan pak kar day"
  33,34,yaad rakho Allah ki ayaat aur hikmat ki baton ko jo tumahray gharon mein sunai jati hain be shak Allah lateef aur bakhabar hai
  33,35,"bilyaqeen jo mard aur jo aurtain muslim hain, momin hain, Mutee farmaan hain, raast baz hain, sabir hain, Allah ke agay jhuknay walay hain, sadqa dainay walay hain, roza rakhnay walay hain, apni sharamgahon ki hifazat karne walay hain, aur Allah ko kasrat se yaad karne walay hain, Allah ne un ke liye mughfirat aur bara ajar muhayya kar rakha hai"
  33,36,kisi momin mard aur kisi momin aurat ko yeh haq nahi hai ke jab Allah aur is ka Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam kisi muamlay ka faisla kar day to phir usay apne uss muamlay mein khud faisla karne ka ikhtiyar haasil rahay aur jo koi Allah aur is ke Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ki nafarmani kere to woh Sarih gumraahi mein par gaya
  33,37,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, yaad karo woh mauqa jab tum is shakhs se keh rahay thay jis par Allah ne aur tum ne ahsaan kya tha ke"" apni biwi ko nah chore aur Allah se dar"" uss waqt tum apne dil mein woh baat chupaye hue thay jisay Allah kholna chahta tha, tum logon se dar rahay thay, halaank Allah is ka ziyada haqdaar hai ke tum is se daro phir jab zaid is se apni haajat poori kar chuka to hum ne is ( mutalqa khatoon ) ka tum se nikah kar diya taakay mominon par apne mun bolay beton ki biwion ke maamla mein koi tangi nah rahay jabkay woh un se apni haajat poori kar chuke hon aur Allah ka hukum to amal mein aana hi chahiye tha"
  33,38,nabi par kisi aisay kaam mein koi rukawat nahi hai jo Allah ne is ke liye muqarrar kar diya ho yahi Allah ki sunnat un sab anbia ke maamla mein rahi hai jo pehlay guzar chuke hain aur Allah ka hukum aik qatee tey shuda faisla hota hai
  33,39,"( yeh Allah ki sunnat hai unn logon ke liye ) jo Allah ke paighamaat pohanchate hain aur usi se drtay hain aur aik khuda ke siwa kisi se nahi drtay, aur muhasba ke liye bas Allah hi kaafi hai"
  33,40,"( logo )Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallamtumahray Mardon mein se kisi ke baap nahi hain, magar woh Allah ke rasool aur Khatim-un-Nabi-een hain, aur Allah har cheez ka ilm rakhnay wala hai"
  33,41,"ae logo! jo imaan laaye ho, Allah ko kasrat se yaad karo"
  33,42,aur subah o shaam is ki tasbeeh karte raho
  33,43,"wohi hai jo tum par rehmat farmata hai aur is ke mulaika tumahray liye duaye rehmat karte hain taakay woh tumhe tarikeon se roshni mein nikaal laaye, woh mominon par bohat meharban hai"
  33,44,jis roz woh is se milein ge unn ka istaqbaal salam se ho ga aur unn ke liye Allah ne bara ba izzat ajar faraham kar rakha hai
  33,45,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, hum ne tumhe bheja hai gawah bana kar, basharat dainay wala aur darane wala bana kar"
  33,46,Allah ki ijazat se uss ki taraf dawat dainay wala bana kar aur roshan chairag bana kar
  33,47,basharat day do unn logon ko jo ( tum par ) imaan laaye hain ke un ke liye Allah ki taraf se bara fazl hai
  33,48,"aur hargiz nah dabo kufar o munafiqeen se, koi parwah nah karo un ki aziat rasani ki aur bharosa kar lau Allah par, Allah hi is ke liye kaafi hai ke aadmi apne mamlaat uss ke supurd kar day"
  33,49,"Ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, jab tum momin aurton se nikah karo aur phir inhen haath laganay se pehlay Talaq day do to tumhari taraf se un par koi iddat lazim nahi hai jis ke poooray honay ka tum mutalba kar sakuu lehaza inhen kuch maal do aur bhallay tareeqay se rukhsat kar do"
  33,50,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, hum ne tumahray liye halal kar den tumhari woh biwiyan jin ke mohar tum ne ada kiye hain, aur woh aurtain jo Allah ki ataa kardah londion mein se tumhari malkiat mein ayen, aur tumhari woh chacha zaad aur phophi zaad aur mamu zaad aur khaala zaad behnain jinhon ne tumahray sath hijrat ki hai, aur woh momin aurat jis ne apne aap ko NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ke liye hiba kya ho agar NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam usay nikah mein lena chahay yeh riayat khalissah tumahray liye hai, dosray mominon ke liye nahi hai hum ko maloom hai ke aam mominon par un ki biwion aur londion ke baray mein hum ne kya hudood aed kiye hain ( tumhe un hudood se hum ne is liye mustasna kya hai ) taakay tumahray oopar koi tangi nah rahay, aur Allah ghafoor o Raheem hai"
  33,51,"tum ko ikhtiyar diya jata hai ke apni biwion mein se jis ko chaho apne se allag rakho, jisay chaho apne sath rakho aur jisay chaho allag rakhnay ke baad apne paas bulaa lau is maamla mein tum par koi muzahiqa nahi hai iss terhan ziyada mutawaqqa hai ke unn ki ankhen thandhi rahen gi aur woh ranjida nah hon gi, aur jo kuch bhi tum unn ko do ge is par woh sab raazi rahen gi Allah jaanta hai jo kuch tum logon ke dilon mein hai, aur Allah Aleem o Haleem hai"
  33,52,"is ke baad tumahray liye doosri aurtain halal nahi hain, aur nah is ki ijazat hai ke un ki jagah aur biwiyan le aao khuwa unn ka husn tumhe kitna hi pasand ho, Albata londion ki tumhe ijazat hai Allah har cheez par nigran hai"
  33,53,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ke gharon mein bulaa ijazat nah chalay aaya karo nah khanay ka waqt taktay raho haan agar tumhe khanay par bulaya jaye to zaroor aao magar jab khana kha lo tu muntashir ho jao, baatein karne mein nah lagey raho tumhari yeh harkatein NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ko takleef deti hain, magar woh sharam ki wajah se kuch nahi kehte aur Allah haq baat kehnay mein nahi sharmaata NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ki biwion se agar tumhe kuch maangna ho to parday ke peechay se manga karo, yeh tumahray aur un ke dilon ki pakizgee ke liye ziyada munasib tareeqa hai tumahray liye yeh hargiz jaaiz nahi ke Allah ke Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ko takleef do, aur nah yeh jaaiz hai ke un ke baad un ki biwion se nikah karo, yeh Allah ke nazdeek bohat bara gunah hai"
  33,54,"tum khuwa koi baat zahir karo ya chupao, Allah ko har baat ka ilm hai"
  33,55,"azwaaj NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ke liye is mein koi muzahiqa nahi hai ke un ke baap, un ke betay, un ke bhai, un ke bhateejay, un ke bhanjay, un ke mil jol ki aurtain aur un ke mamlook gharon mein ayen ( ae oortoo ) tumhe Allah ki nafarmani se parhaiz karna chahiye Allah har cheez par nigah rakhta hai"
  33,56,"Allah aur is ke mulaika NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam par duroood bhaijtay hain, ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, tum bhi un par duroood o salam bhaijho"
  33,57,jo log Allah aur is ke Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ko aziat dete hain un par duniya aur akhirat mein Allah ne laanat farmai hai aur unn ke liye ruswa kin azaab muhayya kar diya hai
  33,58,aur jo log momin mardon aur aurton ko be qasoor aziat dete hain onhon ne aik barray bohtan aur Sarih gunah ka wabaal apne sir le liya hai
  33,59,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, apni biwion aur baityon aur ahal imaan ki aurton se keh do ke apne oopar apni chadoroon ke Palu latka liya karen yeh ziyada munasib tareeqa hai taakay woh pehchan li jayen aur nah satayi jayen Allah taala ghafoor o Raheem hai"
  33,60,"agar munafiqeen, aur woh log jin ke dilon mein kharabi hai, aur woh jo madinah mein hejaan angaiz afwahen phelanay walay hain, apni harkato se baz nah aeye to hum un ke khilaaf karwai karne ke liye tumhe uttha khara karen ge, phir woh is shehar mein mushkil hi se tumahray sath reh saken ge"
  33,61,"un par har taraf se laanat ki bochhaar ho gi, jahan kahin paye jayen ge pakdae jayen ge aur burii terhan maaray jayen ge"
  33,62,"yeh Allah ki sunnat hai jo aisay logon ke muamlay mein pehlay se chali aa rahi hai, aur tum Allah ki sunnat mein koi tabdeeli nah pao ge"
  33,63,"log tum se puchhte hain ke qayamat ki gharri kab aeye gi kaho, uss ka ilm to Allah hi ko hai tumhe kya khabar, shayad ke woh qareeb hi aa lagi ho"
  33,64,behar haal yeh yakeeni amar hai ke Allah ne kafiroon par laanat ki hai aur un ke liye bharakti hui aag muhayya kar di hai
  33,65,"jis mein woh hamesha rahen ge, koi haami o madad gaar nah pa saken ge"
  33,66,"jis roz un ke chehray aag par ulat palat kiye jayen ge uss waqt woh kahin ge ke"" kash hum ne Allah aur Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ki itaat ki hoti """
  33,67,"aur kahin ge"" ae rab hamaray, hum ne apne sardaro aur apne barron ki itaat ki aur unhon ne hamein raah e raast se be raah kar diya"
  33,68,"ae rab, un ko dohra azaab day aur un par sakht laanat kar """
  33,69,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, unn logon ki terhan nah ban jao jinhon ne moose ko azeeyaten di theen, phir Allah ne unn ki banai hui baton se uss ki bra_ea_iat farmai aur woh Allah ke nazdeek ba izzat tha"
  33,70,"ae imaan laane walo, Allah se daro aur theek baat kya karo"
  33,71,Allah tumahray aamaal durust kar day ga aur tumahrayKasoroo-n se dar guzar farmaiye ga jo shakhs Allah aur is ke Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ki itaat kere uss ne barri kamyabi haasil ki
  33,72,"hum ne is amanat ko asmano aur zameen aur pahoron ke samnay paish kya to woh ussay uthany ke liye tayyar nah hue aur is se dar gay, magar ensaan ne usay utha liya, be shak woh bara zalim aur jaahil hai"
  33,73,"iss baar amanat ko uthany ka laazmi nateeja yeh hai ke Allah munafiq mardon aur aurton, aur mushriq mardon aur aurton ko saza day aur momin Mardon aur aurton ki tauba qubool kere, Allah dar guzar frmane wala aur Raheem hai"
